# Searching the web
# source: https://hackernoon.com/cross-platform-productivity-tool-with-terminal-7dd0487ead93#.6oxf3gey7

# This is the most used feature and oh-my-zsh has a perfect plugin, called web-search, that allows me to do this:
# $ ddg how to ride a bicycle   # search duckduckgo
# $ image beautiful bicycle     # search for images
# $ map bicycle store           # search on a map
